Package sk.stuba.fiit.gui

Class MainController

java.lang.Object
sk.stuba.fiit.gui.MainController
public class MainController extends Object
The MainController class represents controller of the Scene (GUI). It consists of a bunch of Buttons, TextFields and Labels. It just controls the Scene (GUI).
